th the existing `cargo receptor complex` term while preserving discoverability of prior wording via broad synonyms.\n+\n+Validation:\n+- Ran `make travis_build` in `src/ontology`\n+- Build passed, including ROBOT/SPARQL validation and reasoning steps\n+\n+Checklist:\n+- [x] PLAN: issue context reviewed and request was clear\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION / AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: validated ontology after edits with `make travis_build`\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: reviewed GO:0061852 and GO:0062137 in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: checked existing cargo receptor complex usage / precedent before editing\n+- [x] EDITS: used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` workflow with a local `terms/` file\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: preserved the existing transport-related relationship and updated the asserted parent appropriately\n+- [x] METADATA: no new term created, so existing metadata retained unchanged\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: committed only `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Updated GO:0061852 to align it with cargo receptor complex usage:\n+- changed the primary label to `retrograde cargo receptor complex, Golgi to ER`\n+- moved it under `cargo receptor complex`\n+- refined the definition accordingly\n+- retained the older `retrograde transporter complex` wording as BROAD synonyms\n+\n+Validation passed with `make travis_build`.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-